Memory Capture Application

The Memory Capture application supports the following:-

  1. Test Framework API
  2. Capture Profile
  3. XWR14xx: MSS Memory Capture Application for XWR14xx
  4. XWR16xx: MSS Memory Capture Application for XWR16xx and DSS Memory Capture Application for XWR16xx
  5. XWR18xx: MSS Memory Capture Application for XWR18xx and DSS Memory Capture Application for XWR18xx
